eated": 1775134614000, "id": "2039688524270559669", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2035041011680911360/3QHKRmms_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Joe Hanneman \ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8", "username": "HanneReports"}, "content": "DOJ says protective order in pipe bombs case covers \u201cIdentifying information, including true names and photographs, regarding government agents who acted in an undercover capacity with respect to this investigation.\u201d \ud83e\udd2f\ud83d\udc40 https://t.co/UrEpQHcSrf", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 179}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZCvcO9B", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 23, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8530789, "raw_content": "If you listen to any of these people, you're part of the problem.\n\nThey don't act in good faith. They're responsible for rightwing infighting, as they spend more time antagonizing Trump than encouraging unity against the communist left. Candace destroyed the unity on the right that was supposed to happen as a result of Charlie Kirk's assassination and I'm convinced that it was deliberate on her behalf.\n\nThese people slam Trump all day and point out all of his mistakes, but offer no help or substance. They'll make it clear that they forsee Republicans losing the midterms, but don't do anything to try and turn the odds around (unlike Scott Presler who is actually trying to help us win), it's almost like they actually want the Democrats to win the midterms and are deliberately helping the left more than the right.\n\nThey don't care about the country. If they did, they'd use their popularity to call for mobilizing and organizing and making sure that Democrats don't win the midterms. But instead, you have Nick Fuentes saying he's going to vote Democrat, and he's doing it to stick it to Trump and the GOP. Listen, I hate the RINOs as much as everyone else, but accelerationism doesn't work and is a suicidal mentality that you absolutely should not subscribe to.\n\nDon't listen to the Woke Right. They gaslight us into thinking that Trump is the problem while they effectively side with the left.", "author": "TheJakeFroggy", "created": 1775139888261, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Porkbut", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "The Woke Right is not to be trusted. And by the Woke Right I mean people like Candace Owens, Nick Fuentes and his army of groypers, Tucker Carlson, Marjorie Taylor Greene, Ian Carroll, Hodgetwins and others.", "last_comment_created": 1775146014969, "content": "<p>If you listen to any of these people, you're part of the problem.</p>\n<p>They don't act in good faith. They're responsible for rightwing infighting, as they spend more time antagonizing Trump than encouraging unity against the communist left. Candace destroyed the unity on the right that was supposed to happen as a result of Charlie Kirk's assassination and I'm convinced that it was deliberate on her behalf.</p>\n<p>These people slam Trump all day and point out all of his mistakes, but offer no help or substance. They'll make it clear that they forsee Republicans losing the midterms, but don't do anything to try and turn the odds around (unlike Scott Presler who is actually trying to help us win), it's almost like they actually want the Democrats to win the midterms and are deliberately helping the left more than the right.</p>\n<p>They don't care about the country. If they did, they'd use their popularity to call for mobilizing and organizing and making sure that Democrats don't win the midterms. But instead, you have Nick Fuentes saying he's going to vote Democrat, and he's doing it to stick it to Trump and the GOP. Listen, I hate the RINOs as much as everyone else, but accelerationism doesn't work and is a suicidal mentality that you absolutely should not subscribe to.</p>\n<p>Don't listen to the Woke Right. They gaslight us into thinking that Trump is the problem while they effectively side with the left.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 23, "score_up": 23, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZCvbpmb", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 35, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8530549, "raw_content": "", "author": "Sunnybats2", "created": 1775131445440, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "getup", "is_video": true, "video_link": "https://www.youtube.com/embed/xfe4H4GcXEc?start=0", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "youtube.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZCvbpmb.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://youtube.com/watch?v=xfe4H4GcXEc&si=N4plhiRYogS23lCi", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "MARK DICE: Gavin Newsom's Wife Out-Wokes Even Him with Insane Rant About YouTube", "last_comment_created": 1775137257988, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 3, "score_up": 35, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"st